column5: Well I went to the post office today to pick up a package.  It was a box full of lures from Lindquist Bros. makers of the Canadian Wiggler.      Lots of assorted lures  Thanks guys, it's much appreciated !!!  Maureen
Congrats on  your great package Maureen! I am sure that it brightend your day right up!
I'm assuming prizes for the Ice fishing for Tyler event.
Yes Wayne, you assume correctly...guess I should have specified that   .  There are over 200.00 worth of lures...like I said, very nice!  Maureen
yes thats great and dont forget the best part...they DO CATCH FISH.....
Great to hear.  That's a great donation for a worthy cause!!!!!!!!!!!!!
